Alison Carroll https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alison_Carroll 0 Alison Laura Carroll (born 21 May 1985) is an English gymnast, model, and actress. She was the live-action model of the video game character Lara Croft from 2008 to 2010. Alison_Laura_Carroll ( born 21_May_1985 ) is an_English_gymnast , model , and actress .
